name: HXRE WE GX AGAIN
description:
Owning this NFT at 00:01UTC on the 26th of February 2022 will move you onto Round 4 of Revebla's X-COVID Lockdown Derby (working title, dont call it that). Interacting in any other way other than holding it at that time will not effect your ability to move forward. Feel free to message me some how if you have any questions. There are still a few rounds left, but if I tell you how many it's just not as fun. 
The unsent ones will be burned soon after the 19th of February.
